Titolo: Rescue (1982 video game)

Anno: 1982

Descrizione: Rescue is a multidirectional shooter arcade video game in which the player navigates a helicopter over the open seas to rescue stranded paratroopers from enemy forces and sharks. It was designed by Chris Oberth  and released by Stern, as an upright arcade machine, in 1982. Rescue combines the dual-stick controls of Robotron: 2084 and the core pick-up/drop-off gameplay of Choplifter.